
  THE TRUTH SHALL BE TOLD AT LAST!!

  
  Remember that business about how the moon landings were faked, how it was
all done on a big Hollywood movie set?

  Well, as it turns out, the rumors were true.  

  But that's not all!


  Apparently, the conspiracy runs even deeper than that, as this photograph
will prove.  This is the Washington Monuement and part of the Capitol
Building, as they really are.  I am perhaps putting my life in danger by
releasing this picture to the public, but the truth MUST be told!

  And the great BenchMaster shall not stray from his appointed path.







  Spread the word while there's still time, my friends.

  You may be the only hope we have.


